Product Description

Cover Girl Eye Enhancers - Quad Eye Shadow Ice Princess #230 contains the advanced stay-put formulas blend effortlessly to bring your eyes out beautifully without overshadowing. Our 4-kit collections of great shades are hand-picked by our make-up pro. Quad. Eye Enhancers Ice Princess #230 : Purple Twilight/ Violet Shiver/ Lilac Frappe/ Moonlit Lilac Application Tips : For best effects never use your fingers to apply eye shadow. Use shadow as you would an eye pencil for softer more subtle effects. Wet your applicator tip and dip in your shadow shade this will create a darker more dramatic shadow effect. Dark eyes look good in grays blues purples and greens. Light eyes look good in brown taupe and bronze shades.
